#### Q24. Which style will change the color of the text?

```html
<cite>Noam Chomsky</cite>
```

- %OPTION% A

```css
cite {
  text-color: cyan;
}
```

- %OPTION% B

```css
cite {
  font-color: cyan;
}
```

- %OPTION% C

```css
cite {
  color: cyan;
}
```

- %OPTION% D

```css
cite {
  text: cyan;
}
```

