#### Q79. In supporting browsers, what would be the effect of using font-display: swap, as in example?

```
@font-face {
    font-family: Helvetica;
    font-display: swap;
}
```

- %OPTION% The browser will show no content until the web font loads.
- %OPTION% The browser will ignore the web font.
- %OPTION% The browser will ignore the web font in a situation where the user has indicated they are saving data.
- %OPTION% The browser will load a system font while waiting for the web font to load.
